      "writtenOn": "2020-04-02T21:59:02Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "In light of what I told you about exception codes, we don’t need this to have SUCH_LOUD_NAMING.\n\n(If we get down to a single call site, we don’t even need for it to be its own function.)",
      "revId": "bbdc8f8d02f4214e63c6bb0636364530159b3083",
